---
description: Testing conventions across the workspace
globs: ["**/*.test.ts", "**/*.test.tsx"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Read `/docs/04-engineering/testing-strategy.md` for the full strategy. Highlights:

- Use shared fixtures from `@gymai/testing` (e.g. `makeFakeWorkoutPlan()`) instead of hand-rolling fixtures per test file.
- `packages/domain` should have close to 100% coverage — it's pure logic, no excuse not to.
- `packages/api` tests must cover malformed AI responses, not just the happy path — the AI is a real source of "wrong shape" failures.
- Don't write tests that only re-assert the type system, and don't snapshot every component's default render.
